title: Prince Andrew | Fox News
description: Prince Andrew is the third child of Queen Elizabeth II and Prince Philip. He is the father of Princess Beatrice and Princess Eugenie with ex-wife, Sarah Ferguson. He stepped back from his public duties in November 2019 overall fallout from his alleged friendship with the late Jeffrey Epstein.
